{"tid":1250374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 遍地開花 ]除左遊行同掟雞蛋，你做左以下事情未？","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T11:00:48.000Z","uid":52200,"like":155,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"59db1892a483bc363509f7fb598173f4092b4b31","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:07:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 擺睇無線，簽有線(或者NOW)。</span></span><br />\n輿論戰真係好重要，好多老一輩嘅人都係無線轉藍之後先變藍血人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. CUT中銀(及其他中字頭)戶口</span></span><br />\n唔好睇少你個1萬蚊、2萬蚊。<br />\n係高槓桿資本主義制度之下，你擺一蚊入銀行，銀行係會借翻十蚊出去，所以銀行並唔係一個穩定性高嘅金融機構，只要有一少部分人覺得中銀服務唔好，中銀都隨時收皮。更何況香港冇法定嘅存款準備金比率，你走1萬蚊，分分鐘中銀就而經借少20萬人仔比中國。<br />\n打倒資本主義！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 登記做功能組別選民</span></span><br />\n懶人包A：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1243929/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1243929/page/1</a><br />\n懶人包B：<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12246935/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%88%BA%E9%87%9D/%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E8%A9%B2%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12246935%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%2588%25BA%25E9%2587%259D%2F%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2588%25A5%2F&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2BhxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=898a0452\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12246935%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%2588%25BA%25E9%2587%259D%2F%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A9%25B2%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%2588%25A5%2F&h=0405f333\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12246935/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%88%BA%E9%87%9D/%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%8D%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E8%A9%B2%E7%95%8C%E5%88%A5/</a><br />\n懶人包C：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%88%BA%E9%87%9D-%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E7%8E%87%E5%81%8F%E4%BD%8E/405554182950962/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%2588%25BA%25E9%2587%259D-%25E5%258A%259F%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%2581%258F%25E4%25BD%258E%2F405554182950962%2F&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2BhxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=f2d8652d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%88%BA%E9%87%9D-%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD%E7%B5%84%E5%88%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%B0%91%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98%E7%8E%87%E5%81%8F%E4%BD%8E/405554182950962/</a><br />\n<br />\n漁農屆嘅何生都只係得一百五十票左右就當選。只要有600個連登仔組織農民突擊隊就有200張選票收佢皮，成本效益仲要高過買盾、買頭盔。<br />\n反攻大陸，正式啟動！！<br />\n#我要走地雞，不要冰鮮雞。<br />\n#港人港漁，發展漁排<br />\n#活化工廈，直立式養豬，對抗豬瘟。<br />\n#香港農業發大財！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4. 制裁黑店</span></span><br />\n雨傘過左5年，喜記仲未收皮，就知道經濟戰唔夠力。<br />\n5年後嘅今日，首要制裁目標係紅磡冰室。<br />\n事件起因：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1216669/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1216669/page/1</a><br />\n制裁名單陸逐有來！<br />\n<br />\n&quot;行不義的，讓他繼續行不義；骯髒的，讓他繼續骯髒；公義的，讓他繼續行公義；聖潔的，讓他繼續被分別為聖。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5. 接濟被捕義士</span></span><br />\n義士嘅付出好大，我o地欠左佢。<br />\n個人認為捐錢比星火會好過民陣。<br />\nLINK: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=Hh5C2Wm8JWR9usSbwEl%2BhxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=9152256b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a><br />\n多多益善，少少唔拘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6. 諗到再講。"},{"pid":"5c735adeef86368a387375709516f18889fcae16","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:07:53.000Z","msg":"香港農業發大財！！！"},{"pid":"b5850346151a9bcb494ac87393b9501707b4e22f","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"香港發大財，林鄭要下台！"},{"pid":"7908ce7f3bd39d5414130f19f6ff90e8fed0678b","tid":1250374,"uid":252510,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"6, 每日用10分鐘, 參與網絡輿論戰<br />\n一個LIKE, 一個COMMENT"},{"pid":"477bbfcf63f6c0bc4e99efa0ae863606b59feb59","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"還我走地雞，不要冰鮮雞！！"},{"pid":"000a4632c8a83cd1a60191ea6427d63ac482b621","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:11:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1250343/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1250343/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n解放香港，mr. president please liberate hong kong!"},{"pid":"4fa5708901f77cced5bfe50113183b024e2fe6de","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7908ce7f3bd39d5414130f19f6ff90e8fed0678b","tid":1250374,"uid":252510,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"6, 每日用10分鐘, 參與網絡輿論戰<br />\n一個LIKE, 一個COMMENT"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"4131e50f5d950e409c757d0a7c27a164604d02ba","tid":1250374,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa570